{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "9347caa8-e91f-4cb9-95e6-9eeda522c2cc", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9347caa8-e91f-4cb9-95e6-9eeda522c2cc@1.pkg/1772597667345/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597667900", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9347caa8-e91f-4cb9-95e6-9eeda522c2cc@1.pkg/1772597667345/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597667900"}, "identifier": "9347caa8-e91f-4cb9-95e6-9eeda522c2cc", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查法律的本质</p>\n\n<p>A:正确。“法生于义，义生于众适，众适合于人心” 强调法律源于众人认可、契合人心，在我国，人民是国家的主人，法律正是体现人民的根本利益和共同意志，该选项符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>B:错误。法律的本质是统治阶级利益和意志的体现，这是所有法律的本质，但题干强调的是我国法律的本质，说法不准确。​​</p>\n\n<p>C：错误。法律体现的是人民的共同意志，并非社会各阶层的全部诉求，“全部诉求” 过于绝对，不同阶层诉求存在差异，法律平衡协调各方利益，并非满足所有诉求。</p>\n\n<p>D：错误。法律虽对社会发展有重要保障作用，但 “任何需求” 说法绝对，社会发展是复杂多元的，法律有其自身的规范范围和局限性，无法满足所有需求。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）“法生于义，义生于众适，众适合于人心，此治之要也。” 这清晰地表明我国法律的本质是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）“法生于义，义生于众适，众适合于人心，此治之要也。” 这清晰地表明我国法律的本质是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9347caa8-e91f-4cb9-95e6-9eeda522c2cc@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143232468", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide